    "methodology": "Healthcare ratings are drawn from HMIP inspection reports, which assess healthcare provision as part of a four-test healthy prison framework. Self-harm data comes from Ministry of Justice Safety in Custody statistics (incidents per 1,000 prisoners). Mental health prevalence is an estimate based on HMIP surveys and academic literature. GP vacancy rates reflect unfilled primary care positions across the prison estate as reported through NHS England Health and Justice commissioning data.",
